To repeat the phrase "Hello world" five times using Python, you can use a for loop. Here's how you can do it:

```python
# This will print "Hello world" five times
for _ in range(5):
    print("Hello world")
```

This code will output:

```
Hello world
Hello world
Hello world
Hello world
Hello world
```
